# Changes from DuckStation

This project applies the following changes to DuckStation Android version `0.1-8969-g611bb8fb4`:

1. Adds the Android `MANAGE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE` permission.
2. Requests “All files access” when the modified application first launches.
3. Changes the preferred user-data location to:
   `/storage/emulated/0/DuckStation`
4. Retains the standard application-specific data location as a fallback when permission is denied.

No affiliation with or endorsement by DuckStation or its developers is claimed.

The original DuckStation APK distributed with this project is unmodified. The changes listed above are produced only after the user separately applies the Xdelta patch.
